1
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:42,760
I never even slept in a woodshed at the Fan house.

2
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,040
We're away from home now.

3
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,519
It's not like being at home.

4
00:01:47,079 --> 00:01:48,359
Come on, just make do.

5
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,560
Then where are you sleeping?

6
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,000
I'll sleep with you.

7
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,680
I'm sleeping with Xiu Gu.

8
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:56,560
Are you coming or not?

9
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,680
Young Master.

10
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,280
The Young Mistress is still waiting for you at home.

11
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,239
I know.

12
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,480
I'm warning you now.

13
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,120
Regarding Yu Zhen...

14
00:02:09,079 --> 00:02:10,400
Don't you go running your mouth.

15
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,359
About this matter,

16
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,400
I'll explain it to her face to face.

17
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:17,039
If you dare gossip all over the place,

18
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:18,879
I'll rip your mouth open.

19
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,599
Everyone thinks you suffered so much out here.

20
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:25,360
But you're actually living quite the carefree life.

21
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:29,719
You only see the thief eating meat,

22
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:32,319
not the thief getting beaten.

23
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,520
Go to sleep.

24
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,599
It's rare for me to travel so far,

25
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,560
and you make me sleep in a woodshed.

26
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,680
Little baby.

27
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,280
Want to see something different?

28
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,960
Little baby.

29
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,479
How do you know who I am?

30
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:17,479
You're a friend of Boss Fan, right?

31
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,879
Who doesn't know that?

32
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,319
Let's go, little baby.

33
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:22,159
Today, let's go drink a different kind of wine.

34
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,879
Are you very expensive?

35
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,960
I'm afraid I didn't bring enough money.

36
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,400
Talking about money is so vulgar.

37
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:32,039
Let's go, let's go.

38
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,000
I'm not bragging,

39
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,159
but our Young Master Fan,

40
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:11,479
he only listens to me.

41
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,280
As long as I

42
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,360
give him

43
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,280
a few instructions,

44
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:21,360
you can open a branch for free.

45
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,800
Baby,

46
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:24,959
then I'll have to repay you properly.

47
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:29,839
Let's try something a little different.

48
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,920
What... what kind of different?

49
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,879
You're so amazing,

50
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,879
surely you have many heroic deeds.

51
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,199
How about you tell me one,

52
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,439
and if I find it fascinating,

53
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:41,120
I'll take off one piece of clothing.

54
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,639
Deal, deal, deal!

55
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:47,800
These stories are like a monk's wooden fish...

56
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,319
plenty, plenty, plenty!

57
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,560
Then hurry up and tell me.

58
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,519
The first one...

59
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:55,199
When our Young Master was in Weiyuan Town,

60
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,879
he was buried alive for colluding with bandits.

61
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,040
It was me

62
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,680
who risked my life to save him.

63
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:03,879
Does that count?

64
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,040
It counts.

65
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,160
Baby, you're so amazing!

66
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,360
I knew it!

67
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:12,720
You have the strong scent of a hero on you.

68
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,800
Off, off, off!

69
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,519
Hey, that's not right.

70
00:05:21,759 --> 00:05:24,360
How come there's another layer underneath?

71
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,839
Let's keep going.

72
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,240
I... I'll strip you down to nothing.

73
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,560
The second story...

74
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:35,279
Our Young Master

75
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:38,120
loves Sichuan Opera.

76
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,519
In Weiyuan Town,

77
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:43,279
he apprenticed under the famous actor

78
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,720
Wen Yan.

79
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,199
Every time he snuck out,

80
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,319
I was the one covering for him.

81
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,279
It's been dozens of pots already.

82
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,279
Not a single one is up to standard.

83
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,399
You...

84
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:03,560
how can you be so thick-headed?

85
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:05,800
Dozens of ingredients, all different amounts.

86
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,120
It'd be a miracle if I could remember them.

87
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,240
Forget it, I can't deal with you.

88
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,360
How about this.

89
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,800
I've written the secret recipe

90
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,480
in this notebook.

91
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,879
You can memorize it.

92
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,360
Memorize?

93
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,959
You scolded me,

94
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:19,439
and I still have to memorize the recipe?

95
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,759
I must be a glutton for punishment.

96
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,399
I said memorize it, so memorize it!

97
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,240
I won't!

98
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,639
Do it!

99
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,879
I said I won't!

100
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,240
Come back and memorize the recipe!

101
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:29,920
Go away!

102
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,560
Xiu Gu, come out and memorize!

103
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:53,120
Memorize the recipe!

104
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,439
How did you know Gan Xia'er had a problem?

105
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:07,680
Every time I teach you to fry the base,

106
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,759
he finds some excuse to run in.

107
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,360
I asked the apprentices,

108
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,199
whenever we fry the base,

109
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,680
he finds an excuse to go to the latrine.

110
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,480
It can't be that much of a coincidence.

111
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:21,240
Then let's go catch him now.

112
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:23,519
Come back.

113
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,720
This Gan Xia'er

114
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,120
is from a poor family too.

115
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,199
When he became an apprentice,

116
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,480
he just wanted to learn a trade.

117
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,639
Let him memorize it.

118
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,279
This...

119
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,959
I copied it from the "Yellow Emperor's Inner Canon".

120
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,160
It won't kill anyone,

121
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,000
and it nourishes yin and strengthens yang.

122
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,879
You always think of everyone else,

123
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,680
but never consider me.

124
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,240
When I see Yu Zhen,

125
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:01,120
I'll tell her about us.

126
00:08:01,319 --> 00:08:02,560
Don't be in such a rush.

127
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:05,079
Yu Zhen is very nice,

128
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,959
she has a soft heart.

129
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,920
Really?

130
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:10,639
Really.

131
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:19,839
Boss Fan,

132
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,800
come, please come inside.

133
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,639
Come.

134
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,360
Boss Fan, please.

135
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:30,680
Good.

136
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,799
What are you looking at? Just sit here.

137
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,080
Sit down.

138
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:56,279
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

139
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,360
Thanks, thanks, thanks.

140
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:00,960
Thanks, thanks, thanks.

141
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,360
Sorry to trouble everyone.

142
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,519
I, Qin, propose a toast to everyone.

143
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:07,159
May you all get promoted and get rich.

144
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:10,759
Wishing Commander Qin a very happy birthday.

145
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,440
Cheers.

146
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,399
Cheers.

147
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,600
Please sit, please sit.

148
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,799
Let the feast begin.

149
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,360
Commander Qin! Commander Qin!

150
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,559
My apologies, my apologies.

151
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:23,600
I, Huo, have arrived late.

152
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:26,159
I went to prepare a big gift for Commander Qin.

153
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,519
That is very thoughtful of you, Young Master Huo.

154
00:09:28,399 --> 00:09:30,600
Knowing Commander Qin is a seasoned opera fan...

155
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:33,440
...I personally went to Weiyuan...

156
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:35,879
...and invited famous performers to liven things up.

157
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,759
I wonder if Commander Qin...

158
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,720
...will like it.

159
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:43,200
When the drums beat, gold pours in.

160
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:47,159
Start the show!

161
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:30,240
Standing at the bow, viewing the beautiful scenery.

162
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:40,320
Thousands of purples and reds fill the land.

163
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:48,399
Gently rocking the boat as it moves slowly.

164
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:59,960
Letting the flowing water carry the boat along.

165
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,720
Bravo! Bravo!

166
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,799
Someone else is celebrating a big birthday...

167
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,080
...what does it have to do with you?

168
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,679
Why are you sulking here?

169
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,879
Did you see clearly?

170
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:22,720
On this invitation...

171
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,440
...my name really isn't written.

172
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,480
They only invited Boss Fan.

173
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:29,679
Even a steamer has upper and lower tiers.

174
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,240
I am the real boss.

175
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,559
I am the General Manager of Dongshihui.

176
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,799
What's the point of joining this bustle?

177
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:38,320
It's all shiny horse dung.

178
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,960
Friendly on the surface, but full of schemes inside.

179
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,759
Even if they invited me, I wouldn't go.

180
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,679
Invite you?

181
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,559
Who are you?

182
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:49,039
I think you've eaten too many corn cakes...

183
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,519
...and are talking nonsense.

184
00:11:51,559 --> 00:11:53,360
You're like a peacock fanning its tail—flattering yourself.

185
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,960
That's enough, you two.

186
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,840
I just feel that...

187
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,399
...this meal of his...

188
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,799
...won't be so easy to eat.

189
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:06,799
You guys keep eating.

190
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,000
I'll go take a look.

191
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,480
And he said he didn't want to go.

192
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:29,200
Quick, find something fast.

193
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,720
To get Master Wen out of here.

194
00:12:32,039 --> 00:12:32,720
Hurry.

195
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:37,759
Today,

196
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:40,480
is the joyous occasion of Commander Qin's birthday.

197
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:43,759
Wen Yan, please join Commander Qin

198
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:44,799
for a couple of drinks.

199
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:50,120
Wishing Commander Qin fortune as the East Sea and longevity as the South Mountain.

200
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,480
Thank you, Wen Yan.

201
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:54,240
Look how soft and delicate Wen Yan's hands are.

202
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:56,159
You sang beautifully just now.

203
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:58,399
I will reward you handsomely later.

204
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:02,039
Wen Yan is truly Weiyuan's famous star.

205
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:06,000
I heard Boss Fan is also from Weiyuan.

206
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:07,720
I wonder if you two

207
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,159
know each other?

208
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:11,559
Don't know him.

209
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,360
Don't know her.

210
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:16,360
I also heard

211
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,000
there was a young master in Weiyuan

212
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,039
who colluded with bandits,

213
00:13:19,639 --> 00:13:21,399
stole his own family's grain,

214
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,960
and was buried alive.

215
00:13:23,559 --> 00:13:25,919
Boss Fan, what a coincidence.

216
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,399
Your surname is also Fan.

217
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:31,240
Young Master Huo, you're rambling.

218
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:33,080
Why are you going so far off topic?

219
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,080
Don't neglect

220
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:36,360
our Wen Yan who came from afar.

221
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:37,480
How about this,

222
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:42,759
I, Qin, will toast Wen Yan first.

223
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,399
Why are you making such a fuss?

224
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,320
Just the two of you drinking,

225
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,360
is so lonely.

226
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:53,039
Why don't we all

227
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:55,200
toast Wen Yan together?

228
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:56,399
That works too.

229
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:58,519
Come, let's all toast Wen Yan.

230
00:14:00,799 --> 00:14:01,279
Cheers.

231
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:07,960
Then please, Wen Yan, take a seat.

232
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:10,840
What's all the commotion now?

233
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:14,879
Today is Commander Qin's big day.

234
00:14:15,399 --> 00:14:17,759
I also want to put on a show

235
00:14:17,759 --> 00:14:20,000
to celebrate Commander Qin's birthday.

236
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,080
Come, come, Wen Yan.

237
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,159
Sit here with me. Sit here.

238
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:24,720
Come.

239
00:14:25,679 --> 00:14:27,159
Commander Qin, don't rush.

240
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,720
Find a chance to leave in a moment.

241
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,600
Someone will pick you up.

242
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,559
Commander Qin,

243
00:14:34,159 --> 00:14:36,759
I'm going on stage now.

244
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,960
Let's go.

245
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:03,639
Coming up, Boss Fan presents.

246
00:15:03,919 --> 00:15:04,759
Boss Fan.

247
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:08,159
Beggars are immortals,

248
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:12,840
Carefree, without worries or troubles.

249
00:15:13,919 --> 00:15:17,000
Good! Good! Good!

250
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:27,960
I give no credit, I owe no debts,

251
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:32,240
Sleeping till the sun is high each day.

252
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:35,279
My daughter-in-law cooks the meal,

253
00:15:35,759 --> 00:15:39,159
Only then do I turn over in bed.

254
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:52,039
It's not hard to learn from me,

255
00:15:52,399 --> 00:15:55,519
First learn to eat, then learn to dress.

256
00:15:55,759 --> 00:16:00,240
Three days no combing, five days no washing,

257
00:16:00,679 --> 00:16:06,000
Naturally you'll become an immortal. An immortal.

258
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:08,240
Good! Good!

259
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,519
Did you see that fat kid just now?

260
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:19,639
What? Who?

261
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,679
Looks like that Fan Sha'er who got buried alive.

262
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:24,679
It's practically seeing a ghost.

263
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:26,320
How could two people look exactly the same?

264
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:28,279
Who cares if he's human or ghost.

265
00:16:28,679 --> 00:16:29,600
Mind your own business.

266
00:16:29,879 --> 00:16:30,679
I tell you, brothers.

267
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:33,159
Young Master Huo was really generous this time.

268
00:16:33,759 --> 00:16:35,039
Earned more than running several jobs.

269
00:16:35,039 --> 00:16:36,039
Let's go, drink at the old tavern ahead.

270
00:16:36,159 --> 00:16:37,200
Let's go, let's go, drink at the old tavern.

271
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,399
Let's go.

272
00:16:40,519 --> 00:16:41,679
Young Master Huo.

273
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:43,919
Oh no.

274
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:45,799
Troupe Leader Wen.

275
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:48,360
I'm a genuine Sichuan opera fan.

276
00:16:48,679 --> 00:16:49,320
Look.

277
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,799
These costumes I've collected.

278
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,480
Every single one is a treasure of mine.

279
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,039
Look.

280
00:16:54,919 --> 00:16:57,480
They... they look better than what you're wearing, Troupe Leader Wen.

281
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,919
Commander Qin, I went the wrong way.

282
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,879
Troupe Leader Wen, Troupe Leader Wen.

283
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,440
Otherwise...

284
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,399
Otherwise, let me change one for you, Troupe Leader Wen.

285
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,159
Troupe Leader Wen.

286
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:05,480
Troupe Leader Wen.

287
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,320
Don't touch me.

288
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:09,840
Let me change one for you, Troupe Leader Wen.

289
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:10,880
Troupe Leader Wen.

290
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,400
Let me change one for you, Troupe Leader Wen.

291
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,079
Let go of me.

292
00:17:15,559 --> 00:17:16,240
What do you mean?

293
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:16,880
Let go of me.

294
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,519
Stop.

295
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,240
I'm just changing clothes for you.

296
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:20,440
I don't mean anything else, Troupe Leader Wen.

297
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,799
Let go of me, don't.

298
00:17:22,759 --> 00:17:23,480
Troupe Leader Wen.

299
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,279
Whenever I see you opera singers,

300
00:17:30,279 --> 00:17:31,279
I get particularly excited.

301
00:17:31,279 --> 00:17:33,119
I just want to connect with you, Troupe Leader Wen.

302
00:17:33,119 --> 00:17:33,759
No other meaning.

303
00:17:33,759 --> 00:17:35,480
Don't, Commander Qin, let go of me.

304
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,119
Let go of me.

305
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:39,880
Troupe Leader Wen.

306
00:17:41,079 --> 00:17:41,480
Let go of me.

307
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,039
Listen to me.

308
00:17:42,039 --> 00:17:43,720
I just simply want to take a nap.

309
00:17:44,039 --> 00:17:45,240
Don't touch me.

310
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:47,920
Don't, Commander Qin, let go of me.

311
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:49,880
Commander Qin, let go of me.

312
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,759
What?

313
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:52,960
Commander Qin.

314
00:17:53,279 --> 00:17:54,079
Drinking.

315
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,160
Get out.

316
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:56,200
Troupe Leader Wen.

317
00:17:56,359 --> 00:17:57,039
Commander Qin.

318
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:59,440
What's so special about opera singers?

319
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,640
I told you to get out.

320
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,720
Don't ruin my good time.

321
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,400
Get out.

322
00:18:03,559 --> 00:18:05,319
Let go of me, don't touch me.

323
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:06,319
Don't touch.

324
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,400
Master Wen, let's go.

325
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,279
Commander Qin

326
00:18:22,799 --> 00:18:23,640
Commander Qin

327
00:18:25,880 --> 00:18:26,440
Young Master

328
00:18:26,519 --> 00:18:27,039
Fan Bao

329
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:28,880
Is this the fastest thing you could find?

330
00:18:29,119 --> 00:18:29,680
Here

331
00:18:31,559 --> 00:18:32,759
Wheelbarrow

332
00:18:33,519 --> 00:18:34,759
It's slower than running

333
00:18:35,039 --> 00:18:37,039
It's so late, where was I supposed to find a sedan chair?

334
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:38,680
You screw-up

335
00:18:40,079 --> 00:18:40,720
Commander Qin

336
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:46,720
Stop

337
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:47,720
What are you doing?

338
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,079
Here, use this

339
00:18:52,519 --> 00:18:53,240
Look at Commander Qin

340
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,839
Why are you grabbing me?

341
00:18:55,839 --> 00:18:56,519
Cut the crap

342
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:58,680
Check on Commander Qin

343
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,400
Behave yourself

344
00:18:59,519 --> 00:19:00,400
Ow, ow, ow

345
00:19:00,519 --> 00:19:01,599
Let go, let go, let go

346
00:19:01,799 --> 00:19:02,640
Master Wen, get on

347
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,680
Fan Bao, let's go

348
00:19:03,839 --> 00:19:04,559
What about you?

349
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,119
Don't worry about me

350
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:06,960
Go

351
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,559
Yu Zhen came to see me

352
00:19:08,559 --> 00:19:09,400
She said she misses you very much

353
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,559
She will definitely wait for your return

354
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,559
Okay. Tell Yu Zhen...

355
00:19:11,759 --> 00:19:12,839
I miss her too

356
00:19:13,119 --> 00:19:14,079
I will definitely go back to find her

357
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:14,640
Go

358
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,920
Why are you pushing it?

359
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,400
I can't ride

360
00:19:20,079 --> 00:19:20,920
Master Wen, you ride

361
00:19:21,039 --> 00:19:22,079
I can't ride either

362
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:23,599
Xuanjizi

363
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,559
Take Master Wen back to Weiyuan immediately

364
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:26,640
I can't ride either

365
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,960
Then how did you get here just now?

366
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:29,920
I pushed it here

367
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:31,640
You screw-up

368
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,599
Master Wen, Fan Bao

369
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,200
Go, go, hurry up and go

370
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,519
Go, go, go

371
00:19:36,519 --> 00:19:37,000
Go

372
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:37,640
Hurry up

373
00:19:39,799 --> 00:19:41,039
Xiu Gu and the others don't know yet

374
00:19:41,359 --> 00:19:42,319
I have to go back and get them

375
00:19:43,279 --> 00:19:44,559
It's too late, it's too late

376
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,519
Xiu Gu saved my life

377
00:19:46,519 --> 00:19:47,960
Save yourself first

378
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:48,960
Only then can you repay the kindness

379
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,839
Don't worry, the secret recipe is still with Xiu Gu

380
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:52,759
Commander Qin wouldn't touch this money tree

381
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:53,759
Listen

382
00:19:53,759 --> 00:19:55,000
I... I'll go back and tell them

383
00:19:55,279 --> 00:19:56,279
If you're leaving, go west

384
00:19:57,119 --> 00:19:57,559
Okay

385
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,519
Wait, wait, wait

386
00:20:01,039 --> 00:20:02,480
I haven't finished speaking yet

387
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:06,960
Take this

388
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:08,640
Remember, keep going west

389
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,359
If you see anyone with a gun, shout "Report"

390
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,039
Okay

391
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,640
I'm counting on you for Xiu Gu

392
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:14,519
No problem

393
00:20:23,599 --> 00:20:25,440
Why are you tying me up?

394
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:28,240
I told you it was that Fan guy who hit him!

395
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:30,079
Boss Fan

396
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,519
You were clearly the only one here

397
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:34,640
Why don't you believe me?

398
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:37,200
How could I possibly harm Commander Qin?

399
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,880
Don't try to shift the blame

400
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:42,000
Ever since Commander Qin and Boss Fan started cooperating

401
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:43,640
You punk have been holding a grudge

402
00:20:43,839 --> 00:20:44,960
Who else could it be but you?

403
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,000
It has to be you

404
00:20:46,519 --> 00:20:47,079
I...

405
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,519
Commander

406
00:20:50,759 --> 00:20:51,319
Commander

407
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,680
Commander, Commander

408
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,640
Commander Qin, you're awake

409
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,000
Catch him! Catch him!

410
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,880
Hear that? Even Commander Qin wants to arrest you

411
00:21:00,079 --> 00:21:02,079
Look clearly, Commander Qin

412
00:21:03,559 --> 00:21:04,200
Named...

413
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,680
Named Fan

414
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,279
See?

415
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:08,039
Hurry up and chase him

416
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,880
You... aren't you going to untie me?

417
00:21:22,759 --> 00:21:23,319
Did you find him?

418
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:23,960
No

419
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:24,920
Go, this way

420
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,039
Nothing

421
00:21:30,039 --> 00:21:30,599
Let's go

422
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,640
Did anyone see him go out?

423
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:34,200
No

424
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,519
Boss.

425
00:22:11,279 --> 00:22:12,720
Which way is west?

426
00:22:12,839 --> 00:22:14,000
Cang Mountain is to the west.

427
00:22:14,319 --> 00:22:15,279
Head towards Cang Mountain.

428
00:23:15,079 --> 00:23:15,920
You messing with me?

429
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,480
Which bastard put the sign up backwards again?

430
00:23:52,119 --> 00:23:52,640
Don't move.

431
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,640
Keep going west.

432
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,359
If you see a gun, shout "Report."

433
00:23:56,839 --> 00:23:57,359
Report!

434
00:23:57,519 --> 00:23:58,240
Report what?

435
00:23:58,319 --> 00:23:59,240
Who are you reporting to?

436
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,200
I'm not holding anything.

437
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:03,440
Nothing at all.

438
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,079
Which hero goes there?

439
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:16,279
Kite flies in the sky, leopard chases on the ground.

440
00:24:20,119 --> 00:24:20,720
Corn.

441
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,359
Eggplant! Don't move.

442
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:24,839
What?

443
00:24:27,519 --> 00:24:29,000
How many people? Speak up.

444
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,839
Just me.

445
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:48,279
I'm back.

446
00:24:48,359 --> 00:24:48,839
You're back.

447
00:24:50,559 --> 00:24:51,160
What are you doing?

448
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:51,640
Move.

449
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,279
Move.

450
00:24:54,759 --> 00:24:56,559
No, what do you mean?

451
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,480
Say something. What do you mean?

452
00:25:07,319 --> 00:25:08,400
Is it up this way?

453
00:25:08,599 --> 00:25:09,079
Move.

454
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:26,359
Move, move, move.

455
00:25:26,599 --> 00:25:27,200
Move it.

456
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,039
Untie me.

457
00:25:47,759 --> 00:25:48,680
That's better.

458
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:58,920
Tie him up.

459
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:00,720
Why are you tying me up again?

460
00:26:37,799 --> 00:26:38,400
Commander

461
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:39,559
Commander

462
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:43,240
Did he talk?

463
00:26:43,319 --> 00:26:43,880
He did.

464
00:26:44,039 --> 00:26:44,920
What did he say?

465
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,680
As soon as I came in, he started hitting me.

466
00:26:50,319 --> 00:26:51,960
How can you treat a brother who risks his life for you...

467
00:26:52,079 --> 00:26:53,039
...so cruelly?

468
00:26:53,559 --> 00:26:56,720
That's what I'm saying.

469
00:26:57,079 --> 00:26:57,920
Commander.

470
00:26:57,920 --> 00:27:00,599
What do you want me to say? Just ask me.

471
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,200
You didn't tell him?

472
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,119
What he needs to confess?

473
00:27:09,720 --> 00:27:11,200
You told me to come in and just do it.

474
00:27:14,839 --> 00:27:16,759
What kind of person is Division Commander Liao?

475
00:27:17,559 --> 00:27:18,680
You know very well.

476
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:22,279
That you could get out of there so easily...

477
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:24,200
They told me...

478
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:26,000
...to be extra cautious.

479
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,160
Commander.

480
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,880
I've followed you for so many years.

481
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,519
I've carried out the most secret missions.

482
00:27:30,759 --> 00:27:33,240
Whoever rebels, I would never rebel.

483
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,920
You don't even trust me?

484
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:36,960
Jizi.

485
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:39,279
I do trust you.

486
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:41,759
Don't you know what kind of person I am?

487
00:27:42,839 --> 00:27:43,839
It's them.

488
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:46,720
They keep pressuring me.

489
00:27:47,359 --> 00:27:48,200
Saying that I just...

490
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:50,000
...crawled out of that adjutant's trap.

491
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,240
I almost lost my life.

492
00:27:53,079 --> 00:27:54,720
Telling me that from now on...

493
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,920
...I should be more cautious.

494
00:27:58,960 --> 00:27:59,640
Jizi.

495
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:01,960
If you have anything to say...

496
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:05,160
...just confess honestly to them.

497
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:07,599
What exactly am I supposed to confess?

498
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:12,559
Tell me the whole story clearly.

499
00:28:16,839 --> 00:28:18,960
I was still wetting the bed at eight.

500
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:23,640
I wore split-crotch pants until I was ten.

501
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:24,680
At fifteen...

502
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,839
Hey, hey, hey.

503
00:28:26,319 --> 00:28:27,599
Are you trying to be smart with me?

504
00:28:29,039 --> 00:28:31,200
Then what age should I start confessing from?

505
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:35,319
Let me give you a hint.

506
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:38,599
Where did that thing on you come from?

507
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,440
What thing on me?

508
00:28:40,839 --> 00:28:42,720
You've already confiscated everything.

509
00:28:44,359 --> 00:28:46,039
Is this place the West?

510
00:28:46,279 --> 00:28:47,720
I want to head West.

511
00:28:48,039 --> 00:28:48,880
If it isn't...

512
00:28:49,119 --> 00:28:52,319
Let me out and I'll start over.

513
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:54,000
Are you playing tricks on me?

514
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:56,240
Do you think this place is a market?

515
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:58,319
Where you can come and go as you please?

516
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:03,119
Xuanjizi.

517
00:29:03,519 --> 00:29:06,279
You bastard, you're wronging me!

518
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,359
I'm the one who's wronged!

519
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:11,279
I earned this money with my own sweat and blood.

520
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,960
I brought it specifically to expand your army.

521
00:29:13,079 --> 00:29:14,359
Are you sure this money...

522
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,680
...was all earned by your hard work?

523
00:29:17,759 --> 00:29:18,680
Others earned some of it too.

524
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,000
I brought it all back.

525
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:21,440
Besides this...

526
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:23,839
...is there nothing else?

527
00:29:27,039 --> 00:29:28,359
Yes, yes, yes. A lucky general.

528
00:29:28,559 --> 00:29:29,519
I found a lucky general for you.

529
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,559
What lucky general?

530
00:29:33,839 --> 00:29:34,599
He didn't come?

531
00:29:38,319 --> 00:29:39,400
You're asking me?

532
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,759
No, Commander, let me explain.

533
00:29:43,039 --> 00:29:45,319
I failed to turn Division Commander Liao's subordinate.

534
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:46,720
So I tricked Division Commander Liao.

535
00:29:46,759 --> 00:29:48,200
I told him I could find him a lucky general.

536
00:29:48,559 --> 00:29:49,400
He believed me.

537
00:29:49,599 --> 00:29:50,680
And let me go.

538
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:51,839
After I got out...

539
00:29:52,039 --> 00:29:53,160
I searched high and low.

540
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,759
And I really did find a lucky general.

541
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:55,680
Of course, Commander.

542
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,720
That lucky general is reserved specially for you.

543
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,200
Along the way...

544
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:00,640
I've been observing this lucky general.

545
00:30:00,799 --> 00:30:02,359
I believe he can definitely assist you.

546
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,400
Where is he?

547
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:16,480
This Sha'er...

548
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:18,680
Where on earth did you run off to?

549
00:30:18,799 --> 00:30:20,759
Who did you catch? It's not sorted out yet.

550
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:21,720
It's a total mess.

551
00:30:22,279 --> 00:30:24,319
Others are doing their duty, yet you have to interfere.

552
00:30:24,559 --> 00:30:25,759
Do you insist on running the show?

553
00:30:25,759 --> 00:30:26,720
Cut the noise.

554
00:30:26,839 --> 00:30:28,319
The Boss decides everything.

555
00:30:28,559 --> 00:30:29,599
Eldest Brother.

556
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,680
Young Master Fan! Young Master Fan!

557
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,319
Brother Fan.

558
00:30:32,319 --> 00:30:33,400
What are you doing here?

559
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:34,279
Brother Fan.

560
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:37,799
In the opera house.

561
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:39,119
We met once.

562
00:30:39,559 --> 00:30:40,559
Scarface.

563
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,680
It was more than just meeting once.

564
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,319
Brother Fan.

565
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:44,519
I really must thank you.

566
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,480
That night when my brothers and I took action...

567
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,960
...thanks to Brother Fan's generous help.

568
00:30:48,279 --> 00:30:49,039
You're too kind.

569
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:49,720
That's right.

570
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,759
He's the one who stole your family's grain.

571
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:54,920
You dummy, you didn't even recognize him.

572
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:57,119
That night, you opened the door for him.

573
00:30:57,119 --> 00:30:58,720
You opened the door for him. It was him.

574
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,759
Never mind all that.

575
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,279
We're all friends now.

576
00:31:02,799 --> 00:31:04,039
Just untie me first.

577
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,279
Brother Fan.

578
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,359
I really feel sorry for you.

579
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:12,400
You'd risk it all for your brothers.

580
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,759
But now you're about to die...

581
00:31:13,839 --> 00:31:14,599
...and where are your brothers?

582
00:31:14,759 --> 00:31:16,559
None of them are stepping up to speak for you.

583
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:18,079
Are you even human?

584
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,160
You stole the grain, yet here you are stirring the pot.

585
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:21,200
Why don't you step up then?

586
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:22,559
If I were his brother...

587
00:31:22,559 --> 00:31:23,799
...I'd definitely step up.

588
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:24,680
See this?

589
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:26,640
I got this scar for my brother.

590
00:31:27,119 --> 00:31:28,480
Save the talk. Untie me.

591
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,240
Move aside.

592
00:31:32,799 --> 00:31:33,880
Why are you here again?

593
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,240
What's the deal with that tiger amulet?

594
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,799
A fortune teller gave it to me.

595
00:31:51,799 --> 00:31:52,759
What about it?

596
00:31:53,079 --> 00:31:54,200
Not talking, huh?

597
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:57,440
What exactly am I supposed to say?

598
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,599
Tiger Ma has orders.

599
00:32:06,079 --> 00:32:08,079
Detain today, execute tomorrow.

600
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,519
Tiger Ma?

601
00:32:13,319 --> 00:32:14,720
This is the Ma Gang?
